title: Frisbee Golf Event
description: SYDE GSA's Frisbee golf event went well!! Looking forward to seeing everyone at the next event. This week we had a fun event planned to make up for bad weather from last term! Thursday was quite nice with a high of 27, so we took advantage of this end of summer weather! We met up near Brubacher House at 3pm - brought our friends and were ready to golf.
